(Dcoburn was the only one to fire on the Brotherhood right?  I just kinda 
skimmed thorugh my mail so someone tell me if I missed anything)

Vehement/Unicron/Reflector/Sun Crusher:




Unicron was behind the shield completely long before the plasma shots were 
fired, and they hit the shield not even coming close to Unicron.

The last of the Brotherhood had gone through the small hole in the shield and 
that hole had closed.  A hatch opened in the side of the ship, and the 
Brotherhood gained entry via the hatch, the entry way closing and locking 
behind them.
